public class ColumnImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements Column

An implementation of the model object 'Column'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Selector
  • Label
  • Sortable
  • Editable
  • Event Active
  • Editable Flag Selector
  • Multi Data Binding
  • Multidata Key Selector
  • Multidata Value Selector
  • Multidata Property Selector
  • Tooltip
  • Active Flag Selector
  • Field Max Length
  • Custom Decorator
